520
00:43:15 --> 00:43:20
you have a high likelihood of
developing the tumor.

521
00:43:20 --> 00:43:25
And it doesn't matter whether the
mutation is coming from your mother

522
00:43:25 --> 00:43:30
or father or whether you're a boy or
