553
00:45:56 --> 00:46:00
but he still passed the mutation
onto his children and they

554
00:46:00 --> 00:46:05
weren't so lucky.
And, finally, what would happen if

555
00:46:05 --> 00:46:09
two individuals who were
heterozygous produced a homozygous

