562
00:46:35 --> 00:46:40
The embryo would never survive
because the gene is important for

563
00:46:40 --> 00:46:44
proliferation control all over the
place.  So the embryo doesn't make

564
00:46:44 --> 00:46:49
it.  So most of the time you cannot
